<text><body>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0001b" n="0001b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b01"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead>僧家禮儀文</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">名旌書䂓</cb:mulu><head>名旌書䂓</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">大宗<g ref="#CB28906"/></cb:mulu><head>大宗<g ref="#CB28906"/></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b04"/><p xml:id="pD64p0001b0401"><g ref="#CB27117"/>佛心印扶宗𡬾教一國諸山名現大徳
<lb ed="D" n="0001b05"/>宗<g ref="#CB28906"/>某堂大<g ref="#CB28906"/>之龕<note place="inline">有<note n="0001b0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">諡【CB】，謚【國圖】</note><app n="0001b0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">諡</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">謚</rdg></app>号則亦書之</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2"><g ref="#CB31402"/>佛人</cb:mulu><head><g ref="#CB31402"/>佛人</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b07"/><p xml:id="pD64p0001b0701"><g ref="#CB31402"/>佛三昧心口相應<g ref="#CB31433"/>林大徳某堂大<g ref="#CB28906"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001b08"/>之龕。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">坐禪人</cb:mulu><head>坐禪人</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/><p xml:id="pD64p0002a0201">叅詳活句<g ref="#CB29766"/>洒神僧山中碩徳某大<g ref="#CB28906"/>之
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/>柩。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">判事人</cb:mulu><head>判事人</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/><p xml:id="pD64p0002a0501">揔領僧風不違䂓繩名現判事某大<g ref="#CB28906"/>之
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/>柩。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">學道人</cb:mulu><head>學道人</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/><p xml:id="pD64p0002a0801">奉佛遺嘱禪教<g ref="#CB31279"/><g ref="#CB31434"/>一國諸山名現山人
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0002b" n="0002b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002b01"/>某大<g ref="#CB28906"/>之柩。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0002b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">平常人</cb:mulu><head>平常人</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0002b03"/><p xml:id="pD64p0002b0301">剃染栖雲<g ref="#CB30130"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>學道清風<g ref="#CB31335"/>子某人之柩。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0002b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">䘮禮奠祭莭次</cb:mulu><head>䘮禮奠祭莭次</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0002b05"/><p xml:id="pD64p0002b0501">凢人臨滅之後先打鍾三下設使者飯剃
<lb ed="D" n="0002b06"/>頭洗浴事一如茶毘文。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002b07"/><p xml:id="pD64p0002b0701">次身軆入龕安置後祭物排設次影子則
<lb ed="D" n="0002b08"/>左邉掛之設壇置香火燈燭次名旌則右
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/>邉立次朝夕祭則影子壇前奉献後龕前
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/>亦以奠祭<note place="inline">平人無影子則作位牌可了</note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pD64p0003a0301">身體<g ref="#CB31270"/>引時行立䂓</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/><p xml:id="pD64p0003a0401">先立威儀龍<g ref="#CB31419"/>一翼扇一雙鳳扇一雙<g ref="#CB30579"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/>盖一雙圎扇一雙毛鞭一拂子一雙次立
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/>𩔊佛輦次引路<g ref="#CB29805"/>次立挽詞幾雙次立昆
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/>布次名旌次立香亭子次〃行立次<g ref="#CB31436"/>司
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/>主僧領諸人分列𤫊龕左右後𩵋山打鐘
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0003b" n="0003b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003b01"/>三下茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>振鈴云<note place="inline">某人𤫊駕</note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003b02"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0003b0201" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">萬挅青山圍𣑽剎</l><l style="text-indent:1em">一竿紅日照十方</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003b03"/><l style="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB31339"/>承三<g ref="#CB30988"/>加持力</l><l style="text-indent:1em">高馭雲車向蓮<g ref="#CB15131"/></l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0003b04"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pD64p0003b0401">次<unclear/>導引聲唱十二佛号</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003b05"/><p xml:id="pD64p0003b0501">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0003b06"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>金臺宝<g ref="#CB31412"/>乗空而來接引此身徃生
<lb ed="D" n="0003b07"/>淨土<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003b08"/><p xml:id="pD64p0003b0801">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a01"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>便随佛号<g ref="#CB29766"/>此界身信受奉行徃生
<lb ed="D" n="0004a02"/>樂國<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a03"/><p xml:id="pD64p0004a0301">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0004a04"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>觀音勢至引導而行随上善人遊<g ref="#CB31430"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a05"/>佛國<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a06"/><p xml:id="pD64p0004a0601">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0004a07"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>経行寶地逰<g ref="#CB29933"/><g ref="#CB31168"/>林大悟三空不聞
<lb ed="D" n="0004a08"/>八苦<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0004b" n="0004b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004b01"/><p xml:id="pD64p0004b0101">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0004b02"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>阿惟越智是不退心彼證無生逹無
<lb ed="D" n="0004b03"/>生忍<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004b04"/><p xml:id="pD64p0004b0401">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0004b05"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>金沙瑩水<g ref="#CB31404"/>𡬾浮空悟四揔持得六
<lb ed="D" n="0004b06"/>波羅密<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004b07"/><p xml:id="pD64p0004b0701">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0004b08"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>遇無量壽得無量光自在優逰光相
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0005a" n="0005a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a01"/>齊<g ref="#CB21717"/><note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a02"/><p xml:id="pD64p0005a0201">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0005a03"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>親近智者同上善人得遇如来便聞
<lb ed="D" n="0005a04"/>授記<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a05"/><p xml:id="pD64p0005a0501">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<lb ed="D" n="0005a06"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>得不動智成自在身五分香燃六度
<lb ed="D" n="0005a07"/>圎滿<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a08"/><p xml:id="pD64p0005a0801">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲阿彌陁佛
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0005b" n="0005b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0005b01"/>惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>還同諸佛大化人天以清淨身演淨
<lb ed="D" n="0005b02"/>妙法<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005b03"/><p xml:id="pD64p0005b0301">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲觀世音菩
<lb ed="D" n="0005b04"/>薩摩訶薩。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005b05"/><p xml:id="pD64p0005b0501">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>大慈大悲大勢至菩
<lb ed="D" n="0005b06"/>薩摩訶薩惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>觀音勢至大<g ref="#CB31339"/>𣴑行指授
<lb ed="D" n="0005b07"/>花臺令生淨土<note place="inline">眾和</note>　歸命阿彌陁佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005b08"/><p xml:id="pD64p0005b0801">次茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>唱舉龕篇次舉龕先立次茶
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0006a" n="0006a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a01"/>毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>擇方而立次無常偈法<g ref="#CB28906"/><g ref="#CB22072"/>無常
<lb ed="D" n="0006a02"/>偈次立五方法<g ref="#CB28906"/>各執方<g ref="#CB29805"/>次立𩵋山諸
<lb ed="D" n="0006a03"/>人<g ref="#CB21717"/>次三動<g ref="#CB17976"/>周囬道塲三匝後龕則𨓍
<lb ed="D" n="0006a04"/>中止<note place="inline">大剎則觧脫門外𨓍中止小剎則月臺中止且舉龕至重但香亭子及名
<lb ed="D" n="0006a05"/>旌舉之三囬亦可</note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a06"/><p xml:id="pD64p0006a0601">次𩵋山又動<g ref="#CB17976"/>唱三<g ref="#CB31404"/>云。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a07"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0006a0701" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">普禮十方常住佛</l><l style="text-indent:1em">普禮十方常住法</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a08"/><l style="text-indent:1em">普禮十方常住僧</l></lg><p xml:id="pD64p0006a0808" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">唱三宝時齋者執名旌各一拜下直又諸庵大
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0006b" n="0006b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0006b01"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>入寂下来時本寺正門外下直可</note>。</p><p xml:id="pD64p0006b0115" cb:place="inline">次𩵋山唱西方大教主
<lb ed="D" n="0006b02"/>南無阿彌陁佛連聲<g ref="#CB31402"/>佛<g ref="#CB31270"/>行又<g ref="#CB31270"/>行時
<lb ed="D" n="0006b03"/>龕橋木上一人<g ref="#CB08888"/>立以大聲唱南無阿彌
<lb ed="D" n="0006b04"/>陁佛則<g ref="#CB31432"/>橋眾人一時唱和徐〃而行次
<lb ed="D" n="0006b05"/>路祭則設遮白幃帳排壇〃上掛影子其
<lb ed="D" n="0006b06"/>影子前設奠祭龕則後馬木上安置又影
<lb ed="D" n="0006b07"/>子壇前讀祭文<note n="0006b0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">云【CB】，𠫔【國圖】</note><app n="0006b0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">云</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">𠫔</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0006b08"/><p xml:id="pD64p0006b0801">維嵗次<note place="inline">某</note>年<note place="inline">某</note>月<note place="inline">某</note>朔越<note place="inline">某</note>日弟子<note place="inline">某</note>謹
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0007a" n="0007a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0007a01"/>以茶果之奠敢昭告于
<lb ed="D" n="0007a02" type="honorific"/><note place="inline">某</note>堂大<g ref="#CB28906"/>之𤫊嗚呼靈變如昨奄及某日
<lb ed="D" n="0007a03"/>音容洞隔何迨追慕身為浮萍住止東西
<lb ed="D" n="0007a04"/>生不做三平死不效神賛<g ref="#CB22526"/>天扣地而益
<lb ed="D" n="0007a05"/>自<g ref="#CB31423"/>〃<g ref="#CB25188"/>将薄奠用訢真𤫊伏惟尚饗<note place="inline">路祭
<lb ed="D" n="0007a06"/>蜼多皆倣此䂓</note>。</p><p xml:id="pD64p0007a0607" cb:place="inline">祭畢後又諸人舉龕<g ref="#CB31270"/>行到闍
<lb ed="D" n="0007a07"/>維所設<g ref="#CB17327"/>日帳後<g ref="#CB31339"/>佛則作高壇掛之影
<lb ed="D" n="0007a08"/>子則下一層作壇掛之又立名旌其兩壇
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0007b" n="0007b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0007b01"/>前香火燈燭茶果胡餅<g ref="#CB21717"/>物排上壇彌陁
<lb ed="D" n="0007b02"/>請白勸供如常後影子壇前山中諸大<g ref="#CB28906"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0007b03"/>着淨衣同誦普賢菩薩行<g ref="#CB31339"/>品身軆𥁞燒
<lb ed="D" n="0007b04"/>之後諸人同時下直可也。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0007b05"/><p xml:id="pD64p0007b0501">龕則<g ref="#CB31339"/>佛壇相去<g ref="#CB31406"/>作壇安置壇前䘮人
<lb ed="D" n="0007b06"/><g ref="#CB21717"/>屈伏泣淚哀〃哭無委曲可〃次舉龕
<lb ed="D" n="0007b07"/>上𧂐<g ref="#CB31411"/>時威儀先立次立引路王<g ref="#CB29805"/>次立
<lb ed="D" n="0007b08"/>五方法<g ref="#CB28906"/>各執方<g ref="#CB29805"/>次立無常偈法<g ref="#CB28906"/>次
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0008a" n="0008a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0008a01"/>立茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>次立䘮者執名旌後舉龕徐
<lb ed="D" n="0008a02"/>徐而行上<g ref="#CB31411"/>則茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>擇方而立五方
<lb ed="D" n="0008a03"/>法<g ref="#CB28906"/>各守其方而立無常偈法<g ref="#CB28906"/>闍維前
<lb ed="D" n="0008a04"/>立次茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>又振鈴云新圎寂<note place="inline">某人<g ref="#CB09566"/>駕</note>
<lb ed="D" n="0008a05"/>無上大涅般圎明常寂照劫火燒海底
<lb ed="D" n="0008a06"/>風鼓山上擊真常寂滅樂涅般相如是
<lb ed="D" n="0008a07"/>一切有為法如夢幻泡影如露亦如電
<lb ed="D" n="0008a08"/>應作如是觀若以色見我以音<g ref="#CB31410"/>求我
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0008b" n="0008b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b01"/>是人行邪道不能見如來。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b02"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0008b0201" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">一<g ref="#CB31402"/>普觀無量刼</l><l style="text-indent:1em">無去無來亦無住</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b03"/><l style="text-indent:1em">如是了知三世事</l><l style="text-indent:1em">超諸方便成十力</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b04"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pD64p0008b0401">茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>振鈴請返魂<g ref="#CB29918"/>語<note place="inline">某人𤫊駕</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b05"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0008b0501" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">真明本軆妙難測</l><l style="text-indent:1em">金鐸𢾗<g ref="#CB31410"/>開覺<g ref="#CB31403"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b06"/><l style="text-indent:1em">月堕秋潭桂影寒</l><l style="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB30115"/>𨈬𣱵<g ref="#CB29766"/>坐𤫊壇</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0008b07"/><p xml:id="pD64p0008b0701">次立圎扇一雙次立引<g ref="#CB31403"/>王<g ref="#CB29805"/>次立名旌
<lb ed="D" n="0008b08"/>還到影子<note place="inline">亦曰位牌</note>壇前安置後唱安座真言
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0009a" n="0009a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0009a01"/>奉茶又法<g ref="#CB28906"/>振鈴云<note place="inline">某𤫊</note>。</p><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pD64p0009a0111">茶偈</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0009a02"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0009a0201" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">趙州茶藥親拜献</l><l style="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB25188"/>表冲情一片誠</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0009a03"/><l style="text-indent:1em">覺醉昏迷三<g ref="#CB30847"/>夢</l><l style="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB30227"/>身直到法王城</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0009a04"/><p xml:id="pD64p0009a0401">次法<g ref="#CB28906"/>及䘮人<g ref="#CB21717"/>執圎扇名旌<g ref="#CB21717"/>物還進
<lb ed="D" n="0009a05"/>闍維所諸威儀及名旌挽詞<g ref="#CB21717"/>𥁞立于𧂐
<lb ed="D" n="0009a06"/>上後茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>唱舉火篇次唱下火篇下
<lb ed="D" n="0009a07"/>火時五方法<g ref="#CB28906"/>一時振鈴唱五方佛請次
<lb ed="D" n="0009a08"/>無常偈法<g ref="#CB28906"/><g ref="#CB22072"/>無常偈次茶毘法<g ref="#CB28906"/>唱奉
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0009b" n="0009b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0009b01"/>送篇。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0009b02"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pD64p0009b0201">切以歿故比丘<note place="inline">某人𤫊駕</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0009b03"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0009b0301" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">既随緣而順寂</l><l style="text-indent:1em">乃依法而茶毘</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0009b04"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0009b0401" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">焚百年弘道之身</l><l style="text-indent:1em">入一<g ref="#CB31403"/>涅般之門</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0009b05"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pD64p0009b0501"><g ref="#CB22526"/>慿尊眾資<g ref="#CB23686"/>覺𤫊<note place="inline">次十<g ref="#CB31402"/>次表白</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0009b06"/><p xml:id="pD64p0009b0601">上来稱<note n="0009b0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">揚【CB】，掦【國圖】</note><app n="0009b0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">揚</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">掦</rdg></app>聖号資薦徃生惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>慧鏡分明
<lb ed="D" n="0009b07"/>真風散彩菩提<g ref="#CB31168"/>裡開敷覺意之花法性
<lb ed="D" n="0009b08"/>海中蕩滌塵心之垢茶傾三奠香<g ref="#CB08650"/>一爐
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0010a" n="0010a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0010a01"/>用薦雲程和南聖眾。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0010a02"/><p xml:id="pD64p0010a0201">次大眾同<g ref="#CB31410"/><g ref="#CB31402"/>佛以待𥁞燒後各散五方
<lb ed="D" n="0010a03"/><g ref="#CB29805"/>則還入火中燒之大眾歸寺中時<g ref="#CB31339"/>佛
<lb ed="D" n="0010a04"/>輦先立次立引<g ref="#CB31403"/>王<g ref="#CB29805"/>次立香亭子影子
<lb ed="D" n="0010a05"/>徐〃而行入扵寺中<g ref="#CB31339"/>佛則卓子掛之影
<lb ed="D" n="0010a06"/>子則佛前叅禮後影殿掛之次香花燈燭
<lb ed="D" n="0010a07"/>餬鉼<g ref="#CB21717"/>物一一献供畢引<g ref="#CB31403"/>王<g ref="#CB29805"/>則燒之
<lb ed="D" n="0010a08"/><note place="inline">此上<g ref="#CB31339"/>佛及影子二輦侍奉出<g ref="#CB31319"/>闍維豦還入寺中徃<g ref="#CB30460"/>事則大宗<g ref="#CB28906"/>如此可<g ref="#CB31576"/>且
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0010b" n="0010b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0010b01"/>平常人則凢事不具但以位牌入香亭子徃<g ref="#CB30460"/>亦可</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0010b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">五方佛請書䂓</cb:mulu><head>五方佛請書䂓</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0010b03"/><p xml:id="pD64p0010b0301">南無東方滿月世<g ref="#CB30847"/>藥<g ref="#CB28906"/>尊佛惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>大慈
<lb ed="D" n="0010b04"/>接引新圎寂<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>青<g ref="#CB31405"/>璃世<g ref="#CB30847"/>中<note place="inline">眾和</note>南無阿
<lb ed="D" n="0010b05"/>彌陁佛<note place="inline">書之青<g ref="#CB29805"/></note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0010b06"/><p xml:id="pD64p0010b0601">南無南方歡喜世界寶勝如来佛惟願大
<lb ed="D" n="0010b07"/>慈接引新圎寂<note place="inline">某靈</note>赤琉璃世界中<note place="inline">眾和</note>南無
<lb ed="D" n="0010b08"/>阿彌陁佛<note place="inline">書之赤<g ref="#CB29805"/></note>。</p>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0011a" n="0011a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a01"/><p xml:id="pD64p0011a0101">南無西方極樂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>阿彌陁佛惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>大慈
<lb ed="D" n="0011a02"/>接引新圎寂<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>白<g ref="#CB31405"/>璃世<g ref="#CB30847"/>中<note place="inline">眾和</note>南無阿
<lb ed="D" n="0011a03"/>彌陁佛<note place="inline">書之白<g ref="#CB29805"/></note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a04"/><p xml:id="pD64p0011a0401">南無北方無憂世<g ref="#CB30847"/>不動尊佛惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>大慈
<lb ed="D" n="0011a05"/>接引新圎寂<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>黑<g ref="#CB31405"/>璃世<g ref="#CB30847"/>中<note place="inline">眾和</note>南無阿
<lb ed="D" n="0011a06"/>彌陁佛<note place="inline">書之黑<g ref="#CB29805"/></note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a07"/><p xml:id="pD64p0011a0701">南無中方<g ref="#CB31435"/>蔵世<g ref="#CB30847"/>毘盧<g ref="#CB17327"/>那佛惟<g ref="#CB31339"/>大
<lb ed="D" n="0011a08"/>慈接引新圎寂<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>黃<g ref="#CB31405"/>璃世<g ref="#CB30847"/>中<note place="inline">眾和</note>南無
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0011b" n="0011b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0011b01"/>阿彌陁佛<note place="inline">書黃<g ref="#CB29805"/></note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0011b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">無常戒偈(造長幡冩之)</cb:mulu><head>無常戒偈<note place="inline">造長幡冩之</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0011b03"/><p xml:id="pD64p0011b0301">夫無常戒者入涅槃之要門越苦海之慈
<lb ed="D" n="0011b04"/>航是故一切諸佛囙此戒故而入涅槃一
<lb ed="D" n="0011b05"/>切眾生囙此戒故而度苦海<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>汝今日逈
<lb ed="D" n="0011b06"/>脫根塵𤫊識獨露受佛無上淨戒何幸如
<lb ed="D" n="0011b07"/>也<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>刼火洞燃大千俱壞須彌巨海磨滅
<lb ed="D" n="0011b08"/>無餘何况此身生老病死憂悲苦<note n="0011b0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">惱【CB】，<g ref="#CB31416"/>【國圖】</note><app n="0011b0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">惱</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><g ref="#CB31416"/></rdg></app>能與
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0012a" n="0012a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a01"/>遠違<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>髮毛𤓰齒皮肉筋骨髄<note n="0012a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">腦【CB】，<g ref="#CB31420"/>【國圖】</note><app n="0012a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">腦</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><g ref="#CB31420"/></rdg></app>垢色皆
<lb ed="D" n="0012a02"/><g ref="#CB31401"/>扵地<g ref="#CB31422"/>㖒膿血津液沫淡精氣大小便
<lb ed="D" n="0012a03"/>利皆<g ref="#CB31401"/>扵水煖氣<g ref="#CB31401"/>火動靜<g ref="#CB31401"/>風四大各
<lb ed="D" n="0012a04"/>離今日亡身當在何<g ref="#CB31406"/><note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>四大<g ref="#CB30579"/>假非可
<lb ed="D" n="0012a05"/>愛惜汝<g ref="#CB30130"/>無始以来至于今日無明<g ref="#CB31400"/>行
<lb ed="D" n="0012a06"/>行<g ref="#CB31400"/>識識<g ref="#CB31400"/>名色名色<g ref="#CB31400"/>六入六入<g ref="#CB31400"/>觸
<lb ed="D" n="0012a07"/>觸<g ref="#CB31400"/>受受<g ref="#CB31400"/>愛愛<g ref="#CB31400"/>取取<g ref="#CB31400"/>有有<g ref="#CB31400"/>生生
<lb ed="D" n="0012a08"/><g ref="#CB31400"/>老死憂悲苦<note n="0012a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">惱【CB】，<g ref="#CB31416"/>【國圖】</note><app n="0012a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">惱</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><g ref="#CB31416"/></rdg></app>無明滅則行滅行滅則
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0012b" n="0012b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0012b01"/>識滅識滅則名色滅名色滅則六入滅六
<lb ed="D" n="0012b02"/>入滅則觸滅觸滅則受滅受<g ref="#CB30499"/>則愛滅愛
<lb ed="D" n="0012b03"/>滅則<g ref="#CB31409"/>滅<g ref="#CB31409"/>滅則有滅有滅則生滅生滅
<lb ed="D" n="0012b04"/>則老死憂悲苦<note n="0012b0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">惱【CB】，<g ref="#CB31416"/>【國圖】</note><app n="0012b0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">惱</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><g ref="#CB31416"/></rdg></app>滅諸法<g ref="#CB30130"/>本來常自寂
<lb ed="D" n="0012b05"/>滅相佛子行道<note n="0012b0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，己【國圖】</note><app n="0012b0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">己</rdg></app>来世得作佛諸行無常
<lb ed="D" n="0012b06"/>是生滅法生滅滅<note n="0012b0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，己【國圖】</note><app n="0012b0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">己</rdg></app>寂滅為樂<g ref="#CB31401"/>依佛陁
<lb ed="D" n="0012b07"/>戒<g ref="#CB31401"/>依逹摩戒<g ref="#CB31401"/>依僧伽戒南無過去<g ref="#CB31404"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0012b08"/>勝如來應供正遍知名行<g ref="#CB30133"/>善逝世間解
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0013a" n="0013a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a01"/>無上士調御丈夫天人<g ref="#CB28906"/>佛世尊<note place="inline">某<g ref="#CB09566"/></note>脫却
<lb ed="D" n="0013a02"/>五隂殻漏子𤫊識獨露受佛無常戒豈不
<lb ed="D" n="0013a03"/>快<g ref="#CB26210"/>豈不快<g ref="#CB26210"/>天堂佛剎随<g ref="#CB31402"/>徃生快活
<lb ed="D" n="0013a04"/>快活。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a05"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0013a0501" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">西來祖意<g ref="#CB31342"/>堂堂</l><l style="text-indent:1em">自淨其心性本<g ref="#CB31431"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a06"/><l style="text-indent:1em">妙體湛然無<g ref="#CB31406"/>所</l><l style="text-indent:1em">山河大地現真光</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">消身<g ref="#CB31406"/>置水<g ref="#CB31407"/>法</cb:mulu><head>消身<g ref="#CB31406"/>置水<g ref="#CB31407"/>法</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a08"/><p xml:id="pD64p0013a0801">五方地以小<g ref="#CB31407"/>貯水每方置之。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0013b" n="0013b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0013b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">碎骨法</cb:mulu><head>碎骨法</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0013b02"/><p xml:id="pD64p0013b0201">真言大蔵十凾樓閣記云人死屍軆雜木
<lb ed="D" n="0013b03"/>嚴之<g ref="#CB31406"/>燒之三日後不洗常布作囊八尺
<lb ed="D" n="0013b04"/>至燒骨所以木筯拾骨入囊向東栁枝翁
<lb ed="D" n="0013b05"/>同斫<g ref="#CB31409"/>作鉢入二鉢其木末作磨子真油
<lb ed="D" n="0013b06"/>三<g ref="#CB09864"/>白炭三斗真抹三匙草席一立<g ref="#CB21717"/>准
<lb ed="D" n="0013b07"/>備上高峯頂盤石上香湯水以木筯𢩾骨
<lb ed="D" n="0013b08"/>洗白炭上燒之時徃生偈然後木筯𢩾骨
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0014a" n="0014a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a01"/>入楊鉢磨子碎抹真油三<g ref="#CB09864"/>瀉骨<g ref="#CB01926"/>以茅
<lb ed="D" n="0014a02"/>似乃草席上塗之軸席石上立燒之時大
<lb ed="D" n="0014a03"/>眾著大衣誦行願品至可散骨亦得。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a04"/><p xml:id="pD64p0014a0401" style="margin-left:1em">頌云。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a05"/><lg xml:id="lgD64p0014a0501" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">法身遍滿百億界</l><l style="text-indent:1em">普放金色照人天</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a06"/><l style="text-indent:1em">應物現形潭底月</l><l style="text-indent:1em">軆圎正<g ref="#CB31412"/><g ref="#CB31404"/>蓮臺</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a07"/><p xml:id="pD64p0014a0701">次<note place="inline">某人靈駕</note>祝願時䘮者大眾前各三拜然後
<lb ed="D" n="0014a08"/>燒席<g ref="#CB01926"/>吹散真末三匙以水交合輪泥粉
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D64.9031.0014b" n="0014b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0014b01"/>骨作丸如大豆施清淵裡大𩵋後以此㓛
<lb ed="D" n="0014b02"/>徳<note place="inline">某靈</note>直至西方還到人生便得出家作大
<lb ed="D" n="0014b03"/>法王身也若如此法碎骨則不勞齋懺水
<lb ed="D" n="0014b04"/>陸亦得。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">舉物誡</cb:mulu><head>舉物誡</head><p xml:id="pD64p0014b0407" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">新靈遺在財物舉示眾人前𥁞賣薦靈是
<lb ed="D" n="0014b05"/>僧家之風也書舉物法為叢林軌式可矣然且賣薦事都在齋者之用心<g ref="#CB23273"/>有書之
<lb ed="D" n="0014b06"/>書之無益故今不書之弟子之行為師豈<g ref="#CB27686"/>然<g ref="#CB26210"/><note n="0014b0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">勿【CB】，匆【國圖】</note><app n="0014b0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">勿</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">匆</rdg></app>為眾人之笑具千萬幸甚</note>。</p></cb:div>
